---
title: Chermoula John Dory & Veggie Tagine with Pearl Couscous, Currants & Mint Yoghurt
description: Sweet and spice and all things nice! Flaky John Dory meets fragrant chermoula and luscious currants, all served over fluffy pearl couscous with a dollop of cool mint yoghurt. It’s a dinner that’s bold, bright, and totally dreamy.

*We’ve replaced the green beans in this recipe with broccoli due to local ingredient availability. y. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
